Package eu.smartdatalake.simsearch.engine

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDistance<V>
    Interface to various distance measures or metrics used in similarity calculations.
    IRequest
    Interface to the various requests (mount, remove, catalog, search).
    IResult
    Interface to the results obtained from similarity search.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OutputWriter
    Auxiliary class that can be used to write search results to a file in CSV format.
    QueryValueParser
    Parser for the various types of query values specified for the attributes in similarity search queries.
    Response
    Generic response involving notifications on submitted requests.
    SearchHandler
    Handles a new multi-attribute similarity search request.
    SearchResponse
    Provides the complete response to a multi-attribute similarity search query, which encapsulates the search results and their similarity matrix.
    SearchResponseFormat
    Formatting the response to a multi-attribute similarity search query to be reported back as a single object (typically in JSON).
